---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About | Obsidian Plugins Guide"
  description="About Obsidian Plugins Guide — independent reviews and tutorials for the Obsidian community."
  canonicalURL="https://notes-automate.com/about/"
>
  <div class="page-heading">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>Independent guides and reviews for Obsidian plugins, themes, and workflows.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="article" style="margin-top:0">
    <div class="content">
      <p>Obsidian Plugins Guide is an independent resource for the Obsidian community. We publish in-depth tutorials, plugin comparisons, and workflow guides to help you get the most out of your vault.</p>
      <p>Our goal is practical, honest coverage — no sponsored rankings, no affiliate padding. Every plugin review is based on real usage.</p>
      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Community plugin reviews and comparisons</li>
        <li>Theme guides and CSS customization</li>
        <li>PKM workflows and productivity systems</li>
        <li>Sync, backup, and publishing setups</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
